@page "/"

<PageTitle>Home</PageTitle>

<h1>Voice Launcher WASM</h1>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-8">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Welcome to Voice Launcher WASM</h5>
                <p class="card-text">
                    This is a Blazor WebAssembly application that provides local browser-based storage and management 
                    of Talon Voice commands and lists using IndexedDB. All data is stored locally in your browser.
                </p>
                
                <h6>Features:</h6>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Local Storage:</strong> All data is stored in your browser's IndexedDB - no server required</li>
                    <li><strong>Talon Command Management:</strong> Import, search, and browse your Talon voice commands</li>
                    <li><strong>List Management:</strong> Import and manage Talon command lists</li>
                    <li><strong>Advanced Search:</strong> Search by command names, scripts, or all fields</li>
                    <li><strong>File Import:</strong> Import .talon files and TalonLists.txt files directly</li>
                </ul>

                <h6>Getting Started:</h6>
                <ol>
                    <li>Go to the <a href="/import" class="text-decoration-none">Import</a> page</li>
                    <li>Upload your .talon files and/or TalonLists.txt files</li>
                    <li>Browse your commands in the <a href="/talon-commands" class="text-decoration-none">Talon Commands</a> section</li>
                    <li>Explore your lists in the <a href="/talon-lists" class="text-decoration-none">Talon Lists</a> section</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">
                <h6 class="card-title">Quick Actions</h6>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="d-grid gap-2">
                    <a href="/import" class="btn btn-primary">
                        <i class="bi bi-upload"></i> Import Files
                    </a>
                    <a href="/talon-commands" class="btn btn-outline-primary">
                        <i class="bi bi-mic"></i> Browse Commands
                    </a>
                    <a href="/talon-lists" class="btn btn-outline-info">
                        <i class="bi bi-list-ul"></i> Browse Lists
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card mt-3">
            <div class="card-header">
                <h6 class="card-title">About IndexedDB Storage</h6>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <p class="card-text small">
                    This application uses your browser's IndexedDB for local storage. 
                    Your data persists between sessions and is private to your browser. 
                    Data is not sent to any server.
                </p>
                <p class="card-text small">
                    <strong>Note:</strong> Clearing your browser data will remove all imported commands and lists.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
